{
  "texts": [
    "With the above reward assignment, we follow the standard PPO algorithm to optimize both the policy and value models.",
    "Combining RS and RLStacking RL on top of RS is shown to be effective (Touvron et al., 2023) for LLM training.",
    "Therefore, we also experiment with this option.",
    "Starting from M dist, we apply RS to fine-tune the model, and then apply RL to further train it.",
    "Training with Holistic RewardsFor comparison purposes, we also analyze model performances when trained with holistic rewards."
  ]
}